---
Source:
  Title: A Year with Rumi
  Translator: Coleman Barks
  Author: Rumi
  ISBN: 978-0060845971
  Publisher: HarperOne
Format: Verse
By: Rumi
Title: Love Moves Away
Description: January 17
---
Pale sunlight,
pale the wall.

Love moves away.
The light changes.

I need more grace
than I thought.
